Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.00,0:00:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}街上都已經裝飾起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.94,0:00:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}慶祝外國節日 說明我國胸懷寬廣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.61,0:00:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這說法聽起來有點可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.93,0:01:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要怎麼裝飾聖誕樹好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.30,0:01:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.67,0:01:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能和友奈一起過聖誕了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.31,0:01:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那當然 只要東鄉哪裡都不去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.84,0:01:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.49,0:01:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.80,0:01:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}園園
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.24,0:01:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們可能是第一次一起過聖誕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這次要大家一起喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.29,0:01:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}過個熱鬧的聖誕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.21,0:01:40.84,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聖誕～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.84,0:01:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聖誕 聖誕
