Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈 有沒有掛歪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.37,0:03:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.78,0:03:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}埼樹也幫我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.07,0:03:32.49,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再稍微靠右一點…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.25,0:03:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她怎麼戴眼鏡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她說是視力下降了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.17,0:03:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}應考生真辛苦 到社辦還讀書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.72,0:03:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}上週各種忙 都沒時間讀書
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這週得補回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.35,0:03:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝罪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.18,0:03:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不是這個意思 別在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.16,0:04:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}比起應考 那個黑洞更要緊嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}剖腹謝罪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對對對 都對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.28,0:04:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最後一題也對 獎勵個大紅花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}風風學姐全都做對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}耶 我真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.37,0:04:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}獎勵時間！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:20.53,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※捏他自某問答節目，主持人在最終環節時會舉右手握拳說出這句台詞。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}答對的話 女子力可以加倍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.37,0:04:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我參加
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是哪門子複習考試啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.83,0:04:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過 風風學姐的女子力先放一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.01,0:04:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的女子力！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.07,0:04:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能做對這麼多就可以了 真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還好有乃木幫忙 畢竟下週還有樹的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以才抓住機會念書嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}姐姐 那不是我的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是鎮上的聖誕活動 學生大合唱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.57,0:04:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好厲害喔 埼樹是學校代表
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還好有友奈陪我練習
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:05:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是實力啦 埼樹自己的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.04,0:05:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這才是我的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}把其他學校的代表全都打倒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.85,0:05:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}目的不對了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.02,0:05:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那為了防止感冒 必須保持最佳狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.22,0:05:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}健康…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.80,0:05:17.39,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}反而更有壓力了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來點營養食品嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就選最有效的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.80,0:05:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}寸寸 寸寸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.08,0:05:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我可以用點寸寸的周邊來賣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真不像你耶 有心事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.31,0:05:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我什麼也沒想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這也不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.55,0:05:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}難道身體哪裡不舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.45,0:05:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈身體不舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.57,0:05:44.31,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}健康…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這怎麼可能管用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.08,0:05:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感覺好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太扯了 怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.23,0:05:53.62,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}健康…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好像是暖和了點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.14,0:05:55.69,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an7}喂 你們要對我們身體做什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:55.05,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn@華康墨字體\frz270\bord0\b0\1c&H1E2F1F&\pos(588,40)}有煩惱一定要跟大家說{\i1}！{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.05,0:05:58.05,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn@華康墨字體\frz270\bord0\b0\fs60\1c&H1E2F1F&\pos(528,38)}有煩惱一定要跟大家說{\i1}！{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}風 書讀完了就來幫忙裝飾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.57,0:06:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}已經裝飾得差不多了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.92,0:06:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}各位…聽我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…我出一個問題！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果蟋蟀偷偷還掉了螞蟻的債務
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}會出現什麼問題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.29,0:06:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}社會科的應用問題？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我在想校刊的猜謎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.47,0:06:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.16,0:06:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那哪算什麼猜謎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}螞蟻有債務這點就很扯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:47.82,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個 其實我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.62,0:07:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是考債權轉移嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.53,0:07:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用青鬼為赤鬼自我犧牲的故事為原型
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.06,0:07:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}仔細考慮一下吧奧古斯特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}救出東鄉的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.79,0:07:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她的使命也轉移到我身上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.48,0:07:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是知道這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉肯定會很傷心的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家好不容易聚在一起 這麼開心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:52.93,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\fn華康POP1體W7\fs30\b0\1c&H4E4D4A&\3c&HF6EEE1&\pos(154,200)\frz12.97\frx356\fry8}聖誕節這名字太外國了沒什麼感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:52.93,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\fn華康POP1體W7\fs30\b0\1c&H4E4D4A&\3c&HF6EEE1&\pos(570,212)\frz40.69\frx352\fry348}叫銀杉節怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.01,0:07:52.93,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\fn華康POP1體W7\fs30\b0\1c&H4E4D4A&\3c&HF6EEE1&\pos(304,340)\frx340\fry354\frz9}沒情調
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:52.93,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\fn華康POP1體W7\fs30\b0\1c&H4E4D4A&\3c&HF6EEE1&\frx356\fry4\pos(302,386)\frz9.44}笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:52.93,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\fn華康POP1體W7\fs30\b0\1c&H4E4D4A&\3c&HF6EEE1&\pos(384,422)\frz17.76\frx344\fry0}我也不太能接受耶…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.02,0:07:52.93,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\fn華康POP1體W7\fs30\b0\1c&H4E4D4A&\3c&HF6EEE1&\pos(562,422)\frz25.66\frx342\fry352}鷲鷲還是鷲鷲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:56.03,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\fn華康POP1體W7\fs30\b0\1c&H4E4D4A&\3c&HF6EEE1&\frz2.427\frx356\fry356\pos(106,516)}好恨自己的文筆不能表現我國的深蘊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是被迫活著的 所以才能留在這一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}公寓的空調怎麼偏偏在這麼冷的天氣壞掉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}昨天我家電燈也突然斷電了 好傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.57,0:08:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}辛苦你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}昨天可真是災難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.96,0:08:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才這點事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}樹昨天把鑰匙搞丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.81,0:08:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我和她只好在大冷天裡找鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:40.14,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}姐姐你別說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去趟便利商店還能變成一場災難
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.11,0:08:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還以為你稍微可靠一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}園子到位的說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}園子 你的手怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.83,0:08:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}戴上桑喬就消失無蹤啦薛丁格
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的手被桑喬吃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.91,0:09:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.15,0:09:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早上被茶壺燙到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.75,0:09:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還好傷得不重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 輕傷而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.65,0:09:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼臘月裡 每個人都過得不順啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.08,0:09:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者社所有人一起去除厄運吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.07,0:09:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別說不吉利的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過可能真有這需要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你別當真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈都還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就好 要是友奈也碰上意外
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就更可疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}又是大赦的錯！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.24,0:09:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.43,0:09:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們也太疑神疑鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好了好了就聊到這裡 大家各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}風學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能借一步說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了 有什麼煩惱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這個 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.67,0:10:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}難不成是戀愛話題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.07,0:10:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那樣的話東鄉會生氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.01,0:10:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不會啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.87,0:10:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那可難說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.62,0:10:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不開玩笑了 有什麼事說說看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其實之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.43,0:10:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}之前哪天？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.84,0:10:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是回收手機的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.21,0:10:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.99,0:10:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其實我將東鄉…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:10:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.21,0:11:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家以前拍的照片之類珍貴的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.61,0:11:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都不在手機裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.51,0:11:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那也沒辦法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.47,0:11:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大赦可能在檢閱中刪掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.95,0:11:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感覺很對不起大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.23,0:11:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}肯定有你們兩個的羞羞照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.21,0:11:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.97,0:11:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那的確沒辦法跟大家商量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.06,0:11:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過你們還真有這種怪異興趣？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.96,0:11:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}風學姐身上有一樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.42,0:12:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唱得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但別在室外唱太久 對嗓子不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好期待樹的演唱啊 我會幫你加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.43,0:12:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就說不只有我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.11,0:12:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過還是謝謝姐姐 我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.25,0:12:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不愧是我妹妹 今天做點暖胃的東西吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.13,0:12:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去一趟超市吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.61,0:12:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.31,0:12:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.59,0:13:19.62,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康POP1體W7\fs30\b0\1c&H4E4D4A&\3c&HE9FAED&\pos(422,388)\frx348\fry354\frz29.32}我在醫院 姐姐被車撞了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:21.61,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康POP1體W7\bord5\fs60\b0\1c&H4E4D4A&\3c&HE9FAED&\frz18.16\frx338\fry0\pos(342,462)}我在醫院 姐姐被車撞了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:30.03,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\fn華康POP1體W7\fs25\b0\1c&H4E4D4A&\3c&HE9FAED&\frx348\fry354\pos(522,166)\frz37.45}我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:30.03,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\fn華康POP1體W7\fs25\b0\1c&H4E4D4A&\3c&HE9FAED&\frx348\fry354\pos(576,184)\frz44.35}小樹冷靜 我馬上來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.51,0:13:30.03,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\fn華康POP1體W7\fs25\b0\1c&H4E4D4A&\3c&HE9FAED&\frx348\fry354\pos(486,274)\frz24.7}我這就去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.52,0:13:30.03,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\fn華康POP1體W7\fs25\b0\1c&H4E4D4A&\3c&HE9FAED&\frx348\fry354\pos(442,336)\frz18.7}我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.96,0:13:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.55,0:13:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.72,0:13:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}風學姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:02.11,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs60\1c&HE6DEE0&\pos(504,106)}新患急診室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她還沒有出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.19,0:14:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我真是太不小心…好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.83,0:14:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.74,0:14:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}風學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.53,0:14:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事 我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}車子突然闖過來 居然連紅燈都不看的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.63,0:14:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.99,0:14:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}樹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 還麻煩大家跑一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你驚動了一群人耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你倒是安慰下我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.21,0:14:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有生命危險吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這你就放心吧 太誇張了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:15:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}應考生怎麼偏偏碰上如此慘事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別說啊 我會趕上應考的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.27,0:15:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一定會趕上的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.79,0:15:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但你要住院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.03,0:15:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只會住一兩週啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.02,0:15:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在醫院請安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.69,0:15:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.83,0:15:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是她的妹妹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.74,0:15:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能和我來一趟 辦個住院手續嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.89,0:15:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.59,0:15:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再見 謝謝你們來看我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.97,0:15:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}目前可以放心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們也小心別受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}該α波出場啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.55,0:15:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別做那種事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.07,0:15:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好失望…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.76,0:15:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}違反交通規則的事 不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.11,0:15:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還好沒有性命危險
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}精靈那時候在幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.62,0:15:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果大家有什麼三長兩短
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.74,0:15:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我肯定保持不了理智
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.99,0:15:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.15,0:16:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別再做什麼國防假面和黑洞了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.30,0:16:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是說真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.67,0:16:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小心別受傷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.95,0:16:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}綠燈了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.21,0:16:15.11,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.42,0:16:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.39,0:16:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果我想把這件事告訴大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.17,0:16:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家都會漸漸陷入不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.38,0:17:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想好好跟風學姐說的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.61,0:17:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她就發生事故了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.97,0:17:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}天之力強大到能影響我們的現實世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.41,0:17:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}無論我們做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.37,0:17:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}影響也一定會換種方式呈現出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}它就是這樣來保持平衡的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.84,0:17:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我身上發生的一切是不能和別人說的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.99,0:17:20.72,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康鋼筆體W2\bord0\b0\1c&HA6AAAC&\frz2.092\pos(112,52)}不說的話
